08:12:09: &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;&amp;lt;ffffffff8112be6d&amp;gt;&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; try_to_free_pages+0x9d/0x130&lt;br/&gt;
08:12:09: &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;&amp;lt;ffffffff81132746&amp;gt;&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; ? next_online_pgdat+0x26/0x50&lt;br/&gt;
